answer.code: My life is very monotonous, the fox said. I huny chickens; men hunt me.All the chickens are just alike, and all men are just alike. And in consequence, I am a little bored. But if you tame me, it will be as if the sun came to shine on my life.

    "visualization"
  ],

    "vl2pdf": "./bin/vl2pdf",

    "tsconfig.json"

    "eslint-config-prettier": "^9.1.0",

    "fast-json-stable-stringify": "~2.1.0",
    "highlight.js": "^11.11.1",
    "jest": "^29.7.0",
    "jest-dev-server": "^11.0.0",
    "mkdirp": "^3.0.1",
    "pako": "^2.1.0",
    "prettier": "^3.4.2",
    "puppeteer": "^15.0.0",
    "release-it": "18.1.2",
    "rollup": "^4.32.1",
    "rollup-plugin-bundle-size": "^1.0.3",
    "serve": "^14.2.4",
